{"tid":442782,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣連結藍牙鍵盤到windows","createTime":"2017-10-21T03:56:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-21T04:34:24.000Z","uid":130271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"50c64823f4d8e39fc826c0dbc6ea49bd4656bde5","tid":442782,"uid":130271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T03:56:05.000Z","msg":"請問點連我個bluetooth keyboard 去windows 呀<br />\n每次開著bluetooth 都detect到 個keyboard 但係就叫我打個passcode<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/21/114710_c0a1685a2517c6f7248c8982678ff1d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F21%2F114710_c0a1685a2517c6f7248c8982678ff1d8.jpg&h=dc385ef4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n問題係windows 冇俾過passcode 我 個bluetooth keyboard 說明書又冇<br />\n同埋正常passcode 應該係用返個bluetooth keyboard 打先可以認證到嘛<br />\n但係部keyboard 又冇反應<br />\n上網睇啲人教打四個零<br />\n我就唯有用個有線keyboard打<br />\n最後當然唔得喇<br />\n<br />\nbtw windows真係好垃圾<br />\nkeyboard 又連唔到 <br />\n就連隻blue tooth mouse 連到後又成撚日斷線<br />\n又成撚日paired 但又冇反應 關機再開機之後後間唔時又會失憶唔記得左個mouse<br />\n憨撚鳩鳩<br />\n相反我部mac 就次次都連到<br />\n一開電腦就自動pair 不知幾方便"},{"pid":"302bd7cfa9f9848e0a0f10e266e83452ea828a25","tid":442782,"uid":130271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T03:59:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f124e8376b169f93836f865c94b45a36b751ee99","tid":442782,"uid":130271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T03:59:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf07081625c609e2916bca745f20a04606e30e1d","tid":442782,"uid":130271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T04:00:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93293b23b8ca21e37c3b1da27f9af1fd7b88953","tid":442782,"uid":130271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T04:01:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df04dba2f0ac068c0b397b9741ef701fc90ebf11","tid":442782,"uid":29063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T04:04:22.000Z","msg":"係keyboard求其打8個no. 撳enter<br />\n再係screen打返一樣嘅no.(可以用on-screen keyboard)"},{"pid":"e7f7bf3f7d8e674369fe57334d58d43c735ad81b","tid":442782,"uid":29063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T04:07:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係keyboard求其打8個no. 撳enter<br />\n再係screen打返一樣嘅no.(可以用on-screen keyboard)</blockquote><br />\n打4個0都好似得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3b66aa5f4ee3b32644583095998de3528d60c20","tid":442782,"uid":130271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T04:15:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係keyboard求其打8個no. 撳enter<br />\n再係screen打返一樣嘅no.(可以用on-screen keyboard)</blockquote><br />\n打4個0都好似得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係哩個辦法都唔得先上黎求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9156e927045ccb83c469aea2c6f9820cd221b7cd","tid":442782,"uid":130271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T04:34:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}